I'm not a literary genius, and I'm sure someone will try and pick this apart or whatever. but you get my point...<br>
whomever you are, your lifestyle is dependent on your countries economic well-being. any country that has a standard of living that provides the financial circumstances and freedoms to access this messageboard probably depends on America's success (through whatever means that may be) through the international economy. maybe you don't like our methods, that's fine. voice your opinions, you're entitled to them. but talk shit and you're just a big fat fucking hypocrite.<br>
and a big /salute to all the men and women in the US and British Armed Forces. I served proudly, and would do it again.<br>
